    • Uses of CellType in de.jannlab.core

      Fields in de.jannlab.core declared as CellType 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      CellType CellArray.celltype
      The CellType gives the functional specification (i.e. the integration and activation function) of the cells in this CellArray.
      static CellType CellType.DMULTIPLICATIVE
      The dmultiplicative cells (delta correction) just pass the input of their the last incoming connection.
      static CellType CellType.LINEAR
      A linear cell with id for activation and sum for integration.
      static CellType CellType.MULTIPLICATIVE
      The multiplicative cell has an id activation and a product integration.
      static CellType CellType.SIGMOID
      A standard sigmoid with sum for integration.
      static CellType CellType.SIGMOID1
      A cell with sigmoid activation of range [-1, 1] and sum integration.
      static CellType CellType.SIGMOID2
      A cell with sigmoid activation of range [-2, 2] and sum integration.
      static CellType CellType.TANH
      A tanh cell with sum for integration.
      static CellType CellType.VALUE
      A simple value cell with no functional specification.
